content:
Now, we're diving into the world of custom stylization using MidJourney. By mastering advanced stylization commands, you can create truly unique and personalized artwork. Whether you're aiming to offer custom digital portraits or simply enhance your artistic skills, this lesson will provide you with the tools you need.

By the end of this lesson, you'll be able to use advanced stylization commands and aspect ratios to create stunning custom styles. Let's get started!
